# root entries below are legacy (older loops wrote them at the workspace root).
/STAGE.md
/NOTES.md
/ITERATION_LOG.md
/LOOP_TASKS.md
/DONE.txt
/BLOCKED.md
# AI Orchestrator loop runtime state
.aio-loop-attachments/
.aio-loop-control/
.aio-loop-state/

